    "en": {
      "title": "President appoints Sagala as Chief of Staff",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Minister Sagala Ratnayake has been appointed to the position of Presidential Chief of Staff.",
        "In addition, Mr. Sagala Ratnayake has also been appointed to the position of Senior Advisor to the President on National Security.",
        "The above appointments have been made by President Ranil Wickramasinghe.",
        "Mr. Sagala Ratnayake also served as the Minister of Law and Order in the Good Governance Government."
      ],
